    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh new-car smell. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come fall in love with your new ride!",
