    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a benchmark for mechanical preservation. Powered by the 3.8L DFI flat-six, it offers visceral, naturally aspirated response paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory mechanical limited-slip differential. The PASM-equipped chassis remains exceptionally tight, with zero degradation in suspension geometry. A clean DME report confirms no overrevs, reflecting meticulous powertrain management. With original paint depth and pristine underpinnings, this example delivers the tactile feedback of a factory-fresh unit. Truly turn-key and collector-grade.",
