    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This meticulously maintained masterpiece has been exclusively garage-kept and pampered by a single owner since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster with zero chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule\u2014the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any creases or wear, and the interior still carries that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every electronic feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a history of preventative maintenance performed strictly at authorized dealerships. This car comes with a complete set of service records, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker. If you are looking for a vehicle that bridges the gap between 'used' and 'new' without compromise, this is the one.",
